NTV journalist Ben Kitili gifted his wife Amina Mude with a brand new car as her birthday gift. The birthday gift comes after the TV anchor had penned a heartwarming birthday message to her. Ben also threw her a birthday party on Saturday at the Empire Lounge in Kilimani. Amina was turning 30 years old. Amina posted the black Mazda SUV on Instagram. "Look at this beauty. My baby got me a new baby #grateful #30thbirthday." SUV prices range between Sh2 million and Sh6 million. Ben Kitili and Amina Mude have been married since 2018 after a three-year engagement. They briefly separated in 2020. This year, they will mark their 4th anniversary. The two met at Tribeka, a famous Nairobi club that was located at the junction of Kimathi Street and Banda Street.